videos.description: Torin Dorn pounds his chest after driving to the hoop while crossing up his defender in the process.
videos.headline: Dorn strikes early with heart-pounding layup

videos.description: Braxton Beverly connects from way beyond the arc to give NC State a 47-38 lead going into the half.
videos.headline: Beverly unloads to increase NC State's lead

videos.description: DJ Funderburk grabs the missed layup from Devon Daniels and slams it home.
videos.headline: Funderburk lays home the jam

videos.description: Garrison Mathews has been hot vs. NC State going 8-of-12 from 3 and scoring 41 points.
videos.headline: Mathews fires from deep, notches 41 points

videos.description: Michael Buckland fires off a no-look bounce pass between 3 defenders to Garrison Mathews who throws down the slam.
videos.headline: Buckland's no-look dish to Mathews leads to massive dunk
